    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310110/extras/5533242629a9c81fa31266e8baf8ff53.avif?t=1741786316\" width=361 height=91 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310110/extras/dca13b7a66b8360155993bcefec117e4.avif?t=1741786316\" width=680 height=261 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this fun and addictive game, your goal is to stack a variety of ingredients to build the tallest burger possible. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each layer of buns, patties, lettuce, cheese, and more must be carefully balanced, and as the burger grows, the challenge increases.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                         <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310110/extras/02655b8b41d8dbf94ade87162d31d39f.avif?t=1741786316\" width=361 height=91 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310110/extras/f7303c563a2e00d4e65168f773183325.avif?t=1741786316\" width=680 height=261 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With simple and intuitive controls, it's a captivating experience that tests your precision and reflexes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310110/extras/4275d938319f67d9d22f76b611508095.avif?t=1741786316\" width=361 height=91 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310110/extras/8416a354d2eae9c33f5b74d23e1a9aca.avif?t=1741786316\" width=680 height=261 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete in the global leaderboard to see who can build the tallest burger tower! Challenge players from around the world and aim for the top spot by stacking ingredients higher than anyone else.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're aiming to beat your own high scores or compete with friends, this quirky burger-stacking adventure promises delicious and guaranteed fun!&quot;</p>",
